  "text": "Note that the window operator itself does not provide storage for data elements. The tuples are directly forwarded and therefore storage needs to be provided by the implementation of the aggregation function instead. This has the advantage that each aggregation function needs to provide storage just for the amount of state it requires, rather than maintaining the entire window. Following [CITATION_1] , we classify aggregation functions as follows:",
